,Recommended,247580,29475215,Posted: 24 January,all,Steph,"Another carpal tunnel creation from Paradox lol. This is pretty much just a cheaper version of Magika but with more annoying problems. Constant clicking off the screen will minimize the game, getting you killed. The teleport spell doesn't work properly, it just rubberbands you back most the time. Enemies box you in, making it impossible to move. Special scrolls only show an icon with no name, so its like a luck of the draw if you have all of them. Friends pick bad robes that continuously murder you. But all in all, if you can get it for cheap and can look beyond all the issues I listed, then I would say grab it. By the way, you think murdering your friends in Magika 1 was bad, this is worse lol."
